  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Contracts Manager (Civil Construction)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a leading player in construction industry. They are looking for a Contracts Manager to join their Contracts Team, in hopes of developing the current high performing team. They are located in the North area.</strong></p><p><strong>Duties of Contracts Manager:</strong></p><ul><li>Support the Senior Contracts Manager/Manager in tender reviews and finalizing tender sums.</li><li>Assist in contract administration, including progress claims, variations, and client correspondence.</li><li>Gather subcontractor quotations for review and approval.</li><li>Monitor and update the Contracts Manager on contractual and site matters.</li><li>Verify subcontractor/supplier claims, prepare payment certifications, and seek necessary approvals.</li><li>Handle final accounts and variation submissions.</li><li>Ensure compliance with the Contracts Department’s quality system.</li><li>Carry out other duties as assigned by management.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min Diploma in Quantity Survey or Civil Engineering</li><li>Min 5 years of contracts management experience in civil construction</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></li><li>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</li><li>EA License No. 19C9682</li><li>EA Reg. No. R22108850 (Chan Mun Mun)</li></ul>",
